snippet.title: Paddington Run App Preview Trailer
snippet.description:
The new Paddington Run is coming soon! Enjoy this fun filled endless runner adventure based on the award-winning Paddington movie.

Soon you’ll be able to see Paddington on a whole new level with the our latest game Paddington Run. Pre-register to unlock some awesome giveaways and train with our mini-game for even more chances to win! http://gmlft.co/PAD_PREREG

******************************
